    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072520/extras/dc3480cff3b13ad48029804f269eeaae.avif?t=1769377290\" width=607 height=65 /></span><br>In Gunz &amp; Golf, a single-player, physics-based game. Your objective is to blast your golf ball to the very top of a handcrafted pixel art course using guns!<br>The omnipresent Developer and the Narrator are there to accompany you to your journey<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072520/extras/e53d6fdfbdc6a44567dc1c41cb987dab.avif?t=1769377290\" width=607 height=65 /></span><br>Strategize your way to the top! Choose from 3 unique guns, each with their own strategic mechanics, to overcome obstacles. The meticulously designed courses offer both satisfying challenges and hilarious frustration.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072520/extras/8bda261bff88a937280535084e28cc59.avif?t=1769377290\" width=607 height=65 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 Unique Guns: Master the 3 high-powered weapons, each offering strategic control over the shots.<br></li><li>Physics-Based Ascent: Expect satisfying challenges and plenty of comedic moments of rage-quits (we've all been there).<br></li><li>Stunning Pixel Art: Traverse a beautiful, handcrafted pixel art course.</li></ul>",
